OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start in north
OL,6,Fthinning and clearing during the
OL,7,Fmorning with bright or sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping, though north coast staying
OL,9,Fcloudier. South and west Highland
OL,10,Fstaying sunny throughout. Somewhat
OL,11,Fcooler, especially in north, still
OL,12,Fquite warm in south.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FSome evening sunshine away
OL,15,Ffrom the far north, then the cloud
OL,16,Fthere will extend south across much of
OL,17,Fthe region tonight, with the odd light
OL,18,Fshower. Lochaber staying clear.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
