OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy start for most, the
OL,6,Fodd light shower, but sunnier over
OL,7,FLochaber, and all areas will brighten
OL,8,Fup with some good sunny spells in the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunny
OL,12,Fspells on Sunday, then cloudier in
OL,13,Fnorthwest with light rain later.
OL,14,FCloudy start Monday then most areas
OL,15,Fbrightening up with some sunshine.
OL,16,FNorthwest cloudy, damp Tuesday,
OL,17,Fsunshine elsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
